lines.text: MAY CONTAIN CONFIDENTIAL WORK PRODUCT, JOINT DEFENSE, OR PRIVILEGED
Subject: Re: Color prints - ad archive
Steve, do you want us to contact David Murphy on the MNAG document production deadline issue or do
you want to make the call. The question in my mind is whether we should let Robins know if we are going
to miss the deadline. We may also want to consider whether any defendant has confronted the problem
before in relation to the MNAG settlement or the MSA
I would probably vote in favor of notice.
MAY CONTAIN CONFIDENTIAL WORK PRODUCT, JOINT DEFENSE, OR PRIVILEGED
